he button label.' => '按钮标签。','The default value from the target set to be used when no explicit mapping for a source value is given.' => '当没有给出显示映射的源值时，从目标设定的默认值将被使用。','The file path to the image.' => '图片文件路径。','The file path to the shared stimulus.' => '共用激勵物的路徑。','The highlighted choice cannot be associated more than %d time(s).' => '突出显示的选择不能被相关联超过%d次数。','The identifier of the choice. This identifier must not be used by any other choice or item variable. An identifier is a string of characters that must start with a Letter or an underscore ("_") and contain only Letters, underscores, hyphens ("-"), period (".", a.k.a. full-stop), Digits, CombiningChars and Extenders.' => '这是考题选项的识别符。 这个标识符不能被任何其他的选项或题目使用。 一个标识符是一个字符串的字符而且必须以字母或下划线("_")为第一个字并且只包含字母，下划线，连字符("-")，句号(".")数字，组合字符和扩展字符。','The identifier of the choice. This identifier must not be used by any other response or item variable. An identifier is a string of characters that must start with a Letter or an underscore ("_") and contain only Letters, underscores, hyphens ("-"), period (".", a.k.a. full-stop), Digits, CombiningChars and Extenders.' => '这是考题选项的识别符。 这个标识符不能被任何其他的选项或题目使用。 一个标识符是一个字符串的字符而且必须以字母或下划线("_")为第一个字并且只包含字母，下划线，连字符("-")，句号(".")数字，组合字符和扩展字符。','The identifier of the modal feedback. This identifier must not be used by any other modal feedback or item variable. An identifier is a string of characters that must start with a Letter or an underscore ("_") and contain only Letters, underscores, hyphens ("-"), period (".", a.k.a. full-stop), Digits, CombiningChars and Extenders.' => '这是模式反馈的标识符。 这个标识符不能被任何其他模式反馈或题目使用。 一个标识符是一个字符串的字符而且必须以字母或下划线("_")为第一个字并且只包含字母，下划线，连字符("-")，句号(".")数字，组合字符和扩展字符。','The identifier of the response identifier. This identifier must not be used by any other response or item variable. An identifier is a string of characters that must start with a Letter or an underscore ("_") and contain only Letters, underscores, hyphens ("-"), period (".", a.k.a. full-stop), Digits, CombiningChars and Extenders.' => '这是模式反馈的标识符。 这个标识符不能被任何其他模式反馈或题目使用。 一个标识符是一个字符串的字符而且必须以字母或下划线("_")为第一个字并且只包含字母，下划线，连字符("-")，句号(".")数字，组合字符和扩展字符。','The IMS QTI Item could not be imported.' => '无法导入IMS QTI题目。','The item needs to be saved before it can be previewed' => '该题目需先储存才可以可以预览','The item of the qti item. It is currently used as a meta data only. It is required by the QTI standard.' => '太多的建议符合您的查询，所以这里只列出几个建议','The left position of the shape relative to the top left corner of the background in pixels. This value may be scaled when the background image size is adapted to it\'s container' => '形状的左部相对于像素为背景的左上角。 当背景图像的尺寸适于容器，这个值可以被缩放。','The loop attribute is used to set continuous play mode. In continuous play mode, once the media object has started to play it should play continuously (subject to maxPlays).' => '环路属性用于设置连续播放模式。 在连续播放模式中，一旦媒体对象已经开始播放，它就应该继续播放(需maxPlays)。','The lower bound of the slider' => '滑块钮的下限','The manifest argument must be an instance of DOMDocument.' => '清单参数必须是DOMDocument的实例。','The maximum number of association is unlimited.' => '关联的使用次数没有限制。','The maximum number of associations that the candidate is allowed to make.' => '考生最多可选的关联。','The maximum number of choices that the candidate is allowed to select.' => '考生可以使用的最多选择数量。','The maximum number of choices this choice may be associated with.' => '这个选择可以与多少其他选择有相关联(最多数量)。','The maximum number of choices this choice may be associated with. If matchMax is 0 there is no restriction.' => '这个选择可以与多少其他选择有相关联(最多数量）。 如果matchMax是0就没有限制。','The maxPlays attribute indicates that the media object can be played at most maxPlays times - it must not be possible for the candidate to play the media object more than maxPlay times. A value of 0 (the default) indicates that there is no limit.' => 'maxPlays属性所述媒体对象可以播放的最多次数。 考生播放媒体对象必须不能多于maxPlay次数。 当指数是0(预设)就表示没有限制。','The MIME-type attribute describes which kind of file may be uploaded.' => 'MIME类型属性描述哪一种文件可以上载。','The minimum number of answers is' => '最少回应的数量是','The minimum number of associations that the candidate is required to make to form a valid response.' => '当考生填写回应时，必须使用多少相关联才是有效的回应。','The minimum number of choices that the candidate is required to select to form a valid response.' => '当考生填写回应时，必须选多少选择才是有效的回应。','The minimum number of choices this choice must be associated with to form a valid response.' => '此选择至少要跟多少其他的选择有相关联才是一个有效的回应。','The number of units corresponding to a step on the slider' => '滑动钮的每一个阶段等于多少个单位','The principle identifier of the item. This identifier must have a corresponding entry in the item\'s metadata.' => '该题目的原理标识符。 这个标识符必须在题目的元数据中有对应的条目。','The purpose for which the rubric is intended to be used. As a reading passage for multiple items, or instructions for a particular section, for example.' => '使用指导语目的。 例如：有多个题目的文章，或作为于某部分的说明。','The QTI class "%1$s" located at line "%2$d" is currently not supported.' => '此QTI类别"%1$s"在于第"%2$d"行已经不被支援。','The selected file is ready to be sent.' => '所选择的文件已预备好，可以发送。','The shape height in pixels. This value may be scaled when the background image size is adapted to it\'s container' => '形状高度以像素为单位。 当背景图像的尺寸适于容器，这个值可以被缩放。','The shape width in pixels. This value may be scaled when the background image size is adapted to it\'s container' => '形状宽度以像素为单位。 当背景图像的尺寸适于容器，这个值可以被缩放。','The target must be an instance of DOMDocument' => '目标必须是DOMDocument的一个实例','The text to be displayed if the image is not available.' => '如果没有提供图像，此文本会显示。','The top position of the shape relative to the top left corner of the background in pixels. This value may be scaled when the background image size is adapted to it\'s container' => '形状的顶部相对于像素为背景的左上角。 当背景图像的尺寸适于容器，这个值可以被缩放。','The upper bound of the slider' => '滑动钮的上限','The ZIP archive containing the IMS QTI Item cannot be extracted.' => '此含有IMS QTI题目的ZIP压缩文件不能被提取。','The ZIP archive does not contain an imsmanifest.xml file or is an invalid ZIP archive.' => '此ZIP压缩文件没有imsmanifest.xml档案或它一个无效的ZIP压缩文件。','There is an incomplete element in your item: 