n selecting child elements each element is normally eligible for selection once only.' => '当选择子元素时，每个子元素通常都只能被选一次而已。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration of the item should still be accepted.' => '考生的回应如果超出题目时限，项目是否还被接受。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration of the section should still be accepted.' => '考生的回应如果超出区域时限，区域是否还被接受。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration of the test part should still be accepted.' => '考生的回应如果超出部分时限，部分是否还被接受。','Whether a candidate\'s response that is beyond the maximum duration should still be accepted.' => '考生的回应如果超出时限，回应是否还被接受。','Who can view the rubric block during the delivery.' => '递送时,谁可以浏览指导语区块。','With Replacement' => '跟取代','An error occured during the import' => '导入时发生了错误','Assembly' => '集会','Assembly import' => '聚集导入','Assigned test-takers' => '已被分配的考生','Assigned to' => '已分配给','Attempts' => '试的次数','Create a new delivery' => '创建一个新的输送','Create a test' => '创建考试','Deliveries' => '递送','Deliveries library' => '递送书库','Delivery is not assigned to any test-taker.' => '此输送没被分配给任何的考生。','Delivery saved' => '递送已储存','Excluded test-takers' => '被排除的考生','Manifest not found in assembly' => '清单中未发现集会','New delivery' => '新的递送','No attempt has been started yet.' => '没有已开始的考试。','No information available' => '没资讯可提供','Prepare, publish deliveries sessions.' => '预备，发布递送时域。','There are currently no tests available to publish.' => '现在没有考试可以发布。','There is currently 1 attempt' => '考生已试了1次','Add All grades' => '添加所有的分数','Add All responses' => '添加所有的回应','Add Test Taker' => '添加考生','All collected variables' => '所有收集的可变数','Anonymise' => '匿名化','Class' => '类别','Delivery' => '递送','Email:' => '电子邮件：','Export CSV File' => '导出CSV文件','Export Table' => '导出表格','First Name:' => '名：','First submitted variables only' => '只要第一个提交的可变数','Grades' => '分数','Label:' => '标签：','Last Name:' => '姓氏:','Last submitted variables only' => '只要最后提交的变数','Login:' => '登入:','Manage Results' => '管理结果',